headline: Cardinal Health to Announce Fourth-Quarter and Year-End Results for Fiscal Year 2025 on August 12
summary: Cardinal Health (NYSE: CAH) plans to release fourth-quarter and year-end financial results for its fiscal year 2025 on August 12, prior to the opening of trading on the New York Stock Exchange. The company will webcast a discussion of these results beginning at 8:30 a.m. Eastern.
